"Change Set:		9793PreferenceBrowser-ar.46PreferenceBrowser-ar.46:Changed default window color pref from white to gray."!!PBWindowColorPreferenceView methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'tfel 2/27/2010 19:34'!initialize	super initialize.	self addActionTitled: 'Bright' target: Preferences selector: #installBrightWindowColors arguments: {} balloonText: 'Use standard bright colors for all windows' translated.	self addActionTitled: 'Pastel' target: Preferences selector: #installPastelWindowColors arguments: {} balloonText: 'Use standard pastel colors for all windows' translated.		self addActionTitled: 'Gray' target: Preferences selector: #installUniformWindowColors arguments: {} balloonText: 'Use gray backgrounds for all standard windows' translated.! !